    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <head type="title"><hi rend="italic">St. Goar</hi>.<ref type="gloss_textual" target="st_goar_poem_glosses_textual.php#STGOARWGCGLOSS" /></head>
                <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                    <l>Past a rock with frowning front,</l>
                    <l>Wrinkled by the tempest&#x02BC;s brunt,<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="st_goar_glosses_contextual.php#STGOARLORELEIGLOSS"/></l>
                    <l>By the <geogName corresp="#RHINE">Rhine</geogName> we downward bore</l>
                    <l>Upon the village of <placeName corresp="#STGOAR">St. Goar</placeName>.</l>
                    <l>Bosomed deep among the hills,</l>
                    <l>Here old <geogName corresp="#RHINE">Rhine</geogName> his current stills,</l>
                    <l>Loitering the banks between,</l>
                    <l>As if, enamoured of the scene,</l>
                    <l>He had forgot his onward way</l>
                    <l>For a live&#x2010;long summer day.</l>
                    <l>Grim the crags through whose dark cleft,</l>
                    <l>Behind, he hath a passage reft;</l>
                    <l>While, gaunt as gorge of hunted boar,</l>
                    <l>Dark yawns the foaming pass before,</l>
                    <l>Where the tormented waters rage,</l>
                    <l>Like demons in their <placeName type="fictional" corresp="#STYX">Stygian</placeName> cage,</l>
                    <l>In giddy eddies whirling round</l>
                    <l>With a sullen choking sound;<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="st_goar_glosses_contextual.php#STGOARWHIRLPOOLGLOSS"/></l>
                    <l>Or flinging far the scattering spray,</l>
                    <l>O&#x02BC;er the peaked rocks that bar his way.</l>
                <pb/><!-- not proofed beyond this point DCH -->
                    <l>&#x2014;No marvel that the spell&#x2010;bound <geogName corresp="#RHINE">Rhine</geogName>,</l>
                    <l>Like giant overcome with wine,</l>
                    <l>Should <hi rend="italic">here</hi> relax his angry frown,</l>
                    <l>And, soothed to slumber, lay him down</l>
                    <l>Amid the vine&#x2010;clad banks, that lave</l> 
                    <l>Their tresses in his placid wave.</l>
                </lg>
            </div>
